SCHEMA: electric/trip_explanation.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.electric.trip_explanation
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Deterministic derived explanation artifact for electrical trip causality inspection.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record trip_explanation
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - explanation_id: id
    - device_id: id
    - fault_ids: list<id>
    - contributing_edges: list<id>
    - thresholds_exceeded: list<map>
    - policy_ids_applied: list<id>
    - generated_tick: int
    - deterministic_fingerprint: sha256
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- Derived only from deterministic fault/protection/decision records.
- No direct Truth mutation side effects.
- Stable hash under equivalent input records/order.
